# Inner tunnel depth shading (gradient)
poly 0.70,1.70 1.30,1.70 1.22,1.36 1.00,1.14 0.78,1.36 gradient-radial #2a1a10 #000000 0.9

# Scattered rubble at mouth
circle 0.62,1.82 0.05 fill #2a1a10 0.85
circle 1.42,1.80 0.045 fill #2a1a10 0.85
circle 0.90,1.86 0.04 fill #1a1008 0.85
circle 1.18,1.82 0.04 fill #2a1a10 0.8
